Instead of repeatedly querying the mapView's LocationDisplay, we can save it to a variable. Although it adds a line of code, it makes the other lines a bit clearer:




        Suggested change











                  mapView.getLocationDisplay().setLocationDataSource(simulatedLocationDataSource);



